Application and Analysis of Rhizopus oryzae Mycelia Extending Characteristic in 
Solid-state Fermentation for Producing Glucoamylase.

Tang X(1)(2), Luo T(2), Li X(2), Yang H(2), Yang Y(1)(2), Li J(1)(2), Xu 
B(1)(2), Huang Z(1)(2).

Author information:
