Pathogenic Role of Immune Cells in Rheumatoid Arthritis: Implications in 
Clinical Treatment and Biomarker Development.

Yap HY(1), Tee SZ(2), Wong MM(3), Chow SK(4)(5), Peh SC(6)(7), Teow SY(8).

